447
01:02:37.625 --> 01:02:39.083
She's not feeling well.

448
01:02:39.166 --> 01:02:40.916
She's taking a nap after taking her pills.

449
01:02:42.625 --> 01:02:44.250
Should I wake her?

450
01:02:48.541 --> 01:02:50.041
Stay for dinner.

451
01:02:51.000 --> 01:02:52.375
