452
01:02:52.541 --> 01:02:55.208
I'm making Kang Som. Net's favorite dish.

453
01:02:56.875 --> 01:02:58.333
Net will be so happy.

454
01:02:58.875 --> 01:03:00.833
Her friends don't visit often.

455
01:03:01.458 --> 01:03:02.875
Wait right here.

456
01:03:22.666 --> 01:03:23.958
