493
01:07:24.541 --> 01:07:27.291
Why did Net's mom still kept
her body around?

494
01:07:29.750 --> 01:07:33.500
She went a little crazy after Net's death.

495
01:07:34.000 --> 01:07:37.500
No matter what anyone said.
she refused to cremate her.

496
01:07:39.000 --> 01:07:41.041
The villagers got scared.

497
01:07:41.666 --> 01:07:44.541
No one wanted to socialize with her.

498
01:09:52.583 --> 01:09:53.833
Can't sleep?

499
