I tried to. Jane.

502
01:10:17.291 --> 01:10:19.500
I believed that one day I would.

503
01:10:25.500 --> 01:10:27.583
But I was fooling myself.

504
01:10:35.958 --> 01:10:37.625
When I broke it off.

505
01:10:38.625 --> 01:10:41.291
I was a total asshole to her.

506
01:10:47.541 --> 01:10:49.625
But she still loved me.

507
01:10:56.416 --> 01:10:58.208
