528
01:15:36.833 --> 01:15:37.875
Asshole!

529
01:15:39.541 --> 01:15:41.166
Why did you leave me?

530
01:15:41.541 --> 01:15:43.208
Don't you love me anymore?

531
01:15:43.416 --> 01:15:45.125
