532
01:15:48.208 --> 01:15:50.375
Where are you going?

533
01:17:33.625 --> 01:17:34.916
Tun.

534
01:17:35.458 --> 01:17:36.625
How are you feeling?

535
01:17:39.500 --> 01:17:41.166
