536
01:17:43.000 --> 01:17:43.833
Tun.

537
01:17:45.583 --> 01:17:46.625
Jane.

538
01:17:46.958 --> 01:17:48.166
Jane.

539
01:17:55.625 --> 01:17:58.625
The abbot said Net's body
will be cremated today.

540
01:18:02.958 --> 01:18:03.958
