541
01:20:05.000 --> 01:20:06.875
-Hello.
-Hello. Jane.

542
01:20:07.291 --> 01:20:08.708
You're here to pick up the photos?

543
01:20:09.166 --> 01:20:10.041
Where's Tun?

544
01:20:10.416 --> 01:20:11.583
He's busy.

545
01:20:12.083 --> 01:20:13.125
Good.

546
01:20:13.541 --> 01:20:16.125
I hope he gets busy often.
so I can see you instead.

547
01:20:23.666 --> 01:20:25.791
You guys went on vacation?

548
01:20:26.750 --> 01:20:28.291
We went to Hua Hin.

549
01:20:28.375 --> 01:20:29.708
When did you go?

550
01:20:30.375 --> 01:20:31.958
Last week.

551
01:20:35.500 --> 01:20:36.791
This photo is...

552
01:20:40.125 --> 01:20:41.125
