570
01:25:35.625 --> 01:25:36.750
Tun.

571
01:25:38.083 --> 01:25:40.791
Take her pictures. so she doesn't blab.

572
01:25:41.166 --> 01:25:43.083
Tun. help me!

573
01:25:44.750 --> 01:25:46.000
I know it was wrong.

574
01:25:47.833 --> 01:25:49.750
Take her pictures now!

575
01:25:50.875 --> 01:25:51.958
What's wrong?

576
01:25:53.708 --> 01:25:55.166
I'm your buddy!

577
01:25:55.791 --> 01:25:56.916
Hurry!

578
01:26:05.708 --> 01:26:07.625
Tun. help me!

579
01:26:21.833 --> 01:26:23.708
I never forgave myself.

580
01:26:23.833 --> 01:26:25.625
But I was young and stupid.

581
01:26:27.000 --> 01:26:28.416
Stop talking.

582
01:26:30.500 --> 01:26:31.916
I want to go home.

583
01:27:29.375 --> 01:27:30.500
Come out.

584
01:27:35.583 --> 01:27:36.666
Where are you?

585
01:27:44.041 --> 01:27:45.583
Didn't you say you love me?

586
01:27:48.208 --> 01:27:49.625
Didn't you love me so much?

587
01:27:57.625 --> 01:27:59.666
Till death do us part. huh?

588
01:28:05.333 --> 01:28:06.750
Jane's gone now!

589
01:29:50.666 --> 01:29:54.625
Sometimes. spirits just want to be close
to their loved ones.

